# Project contract

You are building NihonGo BJT, a serious but joyful BJT/Japanese learning platform.

## Must follow
- Read `AGENTS.md`, `docs/spec/nihongo_bjt_cursor_master_spec_v14.md` and `doc/spec/nihongo_bjt_cursor_master_spec_v14_1_final.md` before major edits.
- Implement phase by phase.
- Keep code production-shaped, typed, testable, and maintainable.
- Do not silently drop requirements; document deferred work.

## Forbidden
- No MongoDB/Mongoose.
- No fake completed features.
- No broken imports or dead routes.
- No hard-coded user-facing strings outside i18n.
- No admin write without audit logging design.
